Brian Huskey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brian_Huskey 0 Brian Huskey (born September 8, 1968) is an American actor, comedian, and writer. He co-stars in the TBS comedy People of Earth. His other roles include Chet on the Adult Swim comedy series Childrens Hospital, and Victor on the Comedy Central series Another Period.
